<body>
  <div class="page-container">
    <nav class="top-navigation" aria-label="Page navigation">
      <a class="nav-button" href="index.html">← Back to Homepage</a>

      <div class="submenu-group">
        <a class="submenu-tab" href="noise-analysis.html">
          <span class="tab-icon" aria-hidden="true">◫</span>
          Noise Analysis
        </a>

        <a class="submenu-tab" href="machine-vision.html">
          <span class="tab-icon" aria-hidden="true">▣</span>
          Machine Vision
        </a>

        <a class="submenu-tab" href="lmm-analysis.html" aria-current="page">
          <span class="tab-icon" aria-hidden="true">Σ</span>
          LMM Analysis
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="page-shell">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1>Linear Mixed Model Analysis</h1>
        <div class="header-line"></div>
      </header>

      <section class="overview">
        <ul class="overview-list">
          <li>
            20명 피험자의 BFI와 BVI 시계열을 Savitzky–Golay 필터로 평활화한 뒤,
            baseline과 1–4 back 구간의 대표값을 계산합니다.
          </li>
          <li>
            피험자 내 반복측정 구조를 고려하기 위해 LMM
            (Linear Mixed Model, 선형혼합모형)을 적용하고,
            N-back load, SDS 및 noise-reduction processing의 영향을 검정합니다.
          </li>
          <li>
            최종 LMM 관측 단위는 개별 frame이 아니라
            <span class="highlight">Subject × Processing × SDS × Load</span> 조합입니다.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Analysis Configuration</h2>

        <div class="card-grid">
          <article class="info-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Participants</h3>
            <span class="metric-value">20 Subjects</span>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>Subject_1–Subject_20</li>
              <li>피험자별 반복측정 자료</li>
              <li>Subject를 grouping factor로 사용</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="info-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Signals</h3>
            <span class="metric-value">BFI &amp; BVI</span>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>BFI: Blood Flow Index</li>
              <li>BVI: Blood Volume Index</li>
              <li>각 metric을 별도의 LMM으로 분석</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="info-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Measurement Depth</h3>
            <span class="metric-value">15 / 20 mm</span>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>SDS: Source–Detector Separation</li>
              <li>Reference category: 15 mm</li>
              <li>20 mm 효과는 15 mm 대비 차이</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="info-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Processing</h3>
            <span class="metric-value">Raw vs Corrected</span>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>RawDarkOnly: dark subtraction 기반</li>
              <li>NoiseReduced: 추가 noise correction</li>
              <li>Reference category: RawDarkOnly</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Processing Pipeline</h2>

        <div class="pipeline">
          <div class="pipeline-step">
            <span class="step-number">1</span>
            <span class="step-title">Signal Import</span>
            <span class="step-text">Excel 첫 번째 열을 time, 두 번째 열을 signal로 읽습니다.</span>
          </div>

          <div class="pipeline-step">
            <span class="step-number">2</span>
            <span class="step-title">Data Cleaning</span>
            <span class="step-text">NaN 및 비수치 값을 제거하고 time 기준으로 정렬합니다.</span>
          </div>

          <div class="pipeline-step">
            <span class="step-number">3</span>
            <span class="step-title">SG Filtering</span>
            <span class="step-text">6001-point, 3rd-order Savitzky–Golay smoothing을 적용합니다.</span>
          </div>

          <div class="pipeline-step">
            <span class="step-number">4</span>
            <span class="step-title">Segmentation</span>
            <span class="step-text">Segments.xlsx의 baseline 및 1–4 back 구간을 추출합니다.</span>
          </div>

          <div class="pipeline-step">
            <span class="step-number">5</span>
            <span class="step-title">Window Mean</span>
            <span class="step-text">각 segment 중앙의 최대 120초 평균을 계산합니다.</span>
          </div>

          <div class="pipeline-step">
            <span class="step-number">6</span>
            <span class="step-title">Normalization</span>
            <span class="step-text">BFI는 log ratio, BVI는 baseline difference로 변환합니다.</span>
          </div>

          <div class="pipeline-step">
            <span class="step-number">7</span>
            <span class="step-title">LMM Inference</span>
            <span class="step-text">고정효과, contrast, LRT 및 random effects를 추정합니다.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Signal Import and Quality Control</h2>

        <div class="card-grid three">
          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Signal File Reading</h3>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>Excel 파일의 첫 번째 열: time</li>
              <li>Excel 파일의 두 번째 열: BFI 또는 BVI</li>
              <li>숫자로 변환할 수 없는 행은 제외</li>
              <li>유효한 sample이 4개 미만이면 처리 실패</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Temporal Ordering</h3>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>유효 sample을 time 오름차순으로 재정렬</li>
              <li>입력 파일의 행 순서가 뒤섞여 있어도 순서 복원</li>
              <li>중복 timestamp와 sampling interval은 별도로 검사하지 않음</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="note-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Sampling Setting</h3>
            <ul class="warning-list">
              <li>설정 sampling rate: <span class="highlight">200 Hz</span></li>
              <li><code>FS</code>는 SG window의 초 환산과 metadata에 사용</li>
              <li>코드 내부에서 resampling 또는 200 Hz 여부 검증은 수행하지 않음</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Savitzky–Golay Filtering</h2>

        <div class="model-block">
          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Local Polynomial Smoothing</h3>
            <div class="equation large">
              \[
                \widetilde{y}(t)
                =
                \operatorname{SG}
                \left(
                  y(t);\ W=6001,\ p=3
                \right)
              \]
            </div>
            <ul class="definition-list">
              <li>Sampling rate: \(F_s=200\ \mathrm{Hz}\)</li>
              <li>Window length: \(W=6001\) samples</li>
              <li>Polynomial order: \(p=3\)</li>
              <li>Boundary mode: <code>interp</code></li>
              <li>Window duration: \(6001/200=30.005\ \mathrm{s}\)</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="note-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Filter Interpretation</h3>
            <ul class="warning-list">
              <li>약 30초 길이의 강한 smoothing으로 빠른 생리 진동을 억제합니다.</li>
              <li>심박 및 호흡 성분보다는 task-level의 느린 변화가 강조됩니다.</li>
              <li>필터는 segment 분리 전에 전체 시계열에 먼저 적용됩니다.</li>
              <li>따라서 task 경계 부근에는 인접 구간 정보가 섞일 수 있습니다.</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Segment Definition and Averaging</h2>

        <div class="card-grid two">
          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Segment Selection</h3>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li><code>Segments.xlsx</code>의 Segment, Start(s), End(s) 열 사용</li>
              <li>End(s) &gt; Start(s)인 구간만 유지</li>
              <li>1st rest, 2nd rest, 3rd rest 구간은 제외</li>
              <li>이름에 baseline 또는 base가 포함된 첫 번째 구간을 baseline으로 선택</li>
              <li>정규표현식 <code>([1-4])back</code>으로 load 1–4 추출</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Centered Analysis Window</h3>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                T_{\mathrm{used}}
                =
                \min
                \left(
                  120\ \mathrm{s},\ T_{\mathrm{segment}}
                \right)
              \]
            </div>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                \overline{y}_{\mathrm{segment}}
                =
                \frac{1}{N}
                \sum_{k=1}^{N}
                \widetilde{y}_k
              \]
            </div>
            <ul class="definition-list">
              <li>120초보다 긴 구간: 중앙 120초 사용</li>
              <li>120초 이하 구간: 전체 구간 사용</li>
              <li>동일 load의 segment가 여러 개면 segment mean을 동일 가중 평균</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Outcome Normalization</h2>

        <div class="card-grid two">
          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">BFI Log-Ratio Outcome</h3>
            <div class="equation large">
              \[
                Y_{\mathrm{BFI}}
                =
                \ln
                \left(
                  \frac{
                    \overline{\mathrm{BFI}}_{\mathrm{task}}
                  }{
                    \overline{\mathrm{BFI}}_{\mathrm{baseline}}
                  }
                \right)
              \]
            </div>
            <ul class="definition-list">
              <li>\(Y=0\): baseline과 동일</li>
              <li>\(Y&gt;0\): task BFI 증가</li>
              <li>\(Y&lt;0\): task BFI 감소</li>
              <li>baseline 또는 task mean이 \(10^{-12}\) 이하이면 제외</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">BVI Baseline-Difference Outcome</h3>
            <div class="equation large">
              \[
                Y_{\mathrm{BVI}}
                =
                \overline{\mathrm{BVI}}_{\mathrm{task}}
                -
                \overline{\mathrm{BVI}}_{\mathrm{baseline}}
              \]
            </div>
            <ul class="definition-list">
              <li>\(Y=0\): baseline과 동일</li>
              <li>\(Y&gt;0\): task BVI 증가</li>
              <li>\(Y&lt;0\): task BVI 감소</li>
              <li>BFI와 달리 logarithmic ratio를 추가로 적용하지 않음</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Model-Input Structure</h2>

        <div class="data-table-wrap">
          <table class="data-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Variable</th>
                <th>Role</th>
                <th>Levels / Definition</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
