      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Primary LMM: Load × SDS</h2>

        <div class="model-block">
          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Noise-Reduced Data Only</h3>
            <div class="formula-label">Model formula</div>
            <div class="equation large">
              \[
                \mathrm{Outcome}
                \sim
                \mathrm{Load}_c
                *
                \mathrm{SDS}
              \]
            </div>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                Y_{ijs}
                =
                \beta_0
                +\beta_1L_{ij}
                +\beta_2S_s
                +\beta_3L_{ij}S_s
                +b_{0i}
                +b_{1i}L_{ij}
                +\varepsilon_{ijs}
              \]
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="info-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Primary Question</h3>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>NoiseReduced 데이터에서 load에 따른 변화가 존재하는가?</li>
              <li>15 mm와 20 mm의 load slope가 서로 다른가?</li>
              <li>평균 load에서 SDS 간 반응 차이가 존재하는가?</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="term-table-wrap" style="margin-top: 20px;">
          <table class="term-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Fixed-Effect Term</th>
                <th>Statistical Meaning</th>
                <th>Interpretation</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <th>Intercept</th>
                <td>\(\beta_0\)</td>
                <td>15 mm, load 2.5에서 예상되는 baseline-normalized Outcome</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>Load_c</th>
                <td>\(\beta_1\)</td>
                <td>15 mm에서 load가 한 단계 증가할 때의 변화</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>C(SDS)[T.20mm]</th>
                <td>\(\beta_2\)</td>
                <td>평균 load에서 20 mm − 15 mm 차이</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>Load_c:C(SDS)[T.20mm]</th>
                <td>\(\beta_3\)</td>
                <td>20 mm slope − 15 mm slope</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Primary Linear Contrasts</h2>

        <div class="card-grid two">
          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Load Slopes</h3>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                \mathrm{Slope}_{15\,mm}=\beta_1
              \]
            </div>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                \mathrm{Slope}_{20\,mm}=\beta_1+\beta_3
              \]
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Between-SDS Contrasts</h3>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                \Delta\mathrm{Slope}_{20-15}=\beta_3
              \]
            </div>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                \Delta\mathrm{SDS}_{20-15}\big|_{L_c=0}=\beta_2
              \]
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Secondary LMM: Load × Processing</h2>

        <div class="model-block">
          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">RawDarkOnly and NoiseReduced</h3>
            <div class="formula-label">Model formula</div>
            <div class="equation large">
              \[
                \mathrm{Outcome}
                \sim
                \mathrm{Load}_c
                *
                \mathrm{Processing}
                +
                \mathrm{SDS}
              \]
            </div>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                Y
                =
                \beta_0+\beta_1L+\beta_2P
                +\beta_3LP+\beta_4S
                +b_0+b_1L+\varepsilon
              \]
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="info-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Secondary Question</h3>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>RawDarkOnly에서 load slope가 존재하는가?</li>
              <li>NoiseReduced에서 load slope가 존재하는가?</li>
              <li>두 processing의 load slope가 서로 다른가?</li>
              <li>SDS를 보정한 processing 평균 차이가 존재하는가?</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="term-table-wrap" style="margin-top: 20px;">
          <table class="term-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Fixed-Effect Term</th>
                <th>Interpretation</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <th>Intercept</th>
                <td>RawDarkOnly, 15 mm, load 2.5에서 예상되는 Outcome</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>Load_c</th>
                <td>RawDarkOnly에서 load가 한 단계 증가할 때의 변화</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>C(Processing)[T.NoiseReduced]</th>
                <td>평균 load에서 NoiseReduced − RawDarkOnly 차이</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>Load_c:C(Processing)[T.NoiseReduced]</th>
                <td>NoiseReduced slope − RawDarkOnly slope</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>C(SDS)[T.20mm]</th>
                <td>Load와 Processing을 보정한 평균적인 20 mm − 15 mm 차이</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="callout warning">
          이 Secondary model에는 Processing × SDS, Load × SDS 및
          Load × Processing × SDS interaction이 없습니다. 따라서
          noise-reduction 효과가 15 mm와 20 mm에서 서로 다른지는 이 모델만으로 직접 검정하지 않습니다.
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Random Effects and Model Fitting</h2>

        <div class="card-grid three">
          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Initial Random Structure</h3>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                (1+\mathrm{Load}_c\mid\mathrm{Subject})
              \]
            </div>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>피험자별 random intercept</li>
              <li>피험자별 random load slope</li>
              <li>intercept–slope covariance</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Fallback Structure</h3>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                (1\mid\mathrm{Subject})
              \]
            </div>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>random-slope model 실패 시 적용</li>
              <li>피험자별 평균 수준 차이만 모델링</li>
              <li>최소 2개 이상의 load를 가진 subject만 유지</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Optimization</h3>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>Estimation: Maximum Likelihood</li>
              <li>REML: False</li>
              <li>Optimizers: L-BFGS, Powell, CG</li>
              <li>Maximum iterations: 2000</li>
              <li>수렴 시도와 warning을 Excel에 기록</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Statistical Inference</h2>

        <div class="card-grid three">
          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Wald z Test</h3>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                z=\frac{\widehat{\beta}}{SE(\widehat{\beta})}
              \]
            </div>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                p=2\Phi(-|z|)
              \]
            </div>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                CI_{95\%}=\widehat{\beta}\pm1.96SE
              \]
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Likelihood-Ratio Test</h3>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                LR=2\left(\ell_{full}-\ell_{reduced}\right)
              \]
            </div>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>Full model과 nested reduced model 비교</li>
              <li>동일한 random-effect structure 사용</li>
              <li>두 모델 모두 수렴하고 관측 수가 같을 때 유효</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">BFI Effect Conversion</h3>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                \mathrm{Ratio}=e^{\widehat{\beta}}
              \]
            </div>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                \%\Delta=100\left(e^{\widehat{\beta}}-1\right)
              \]
            </div>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>BFI log-ratio coefficient만 변환</li>
              <li>BVI coefficient에는 적용하지 않음</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Likelihood-Ratio Tests</h2>

        <div class="card-grid two">
          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Primary Model Tests</h3>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li><span class="highlight">Load × SDS</span>: interaction 제거 모델과 비교</li>
              <li><span class="highlight">All load terms</span>: load main effect와 interaction 동시 제거</li>
              <li><span class="highlight">All SDS terms</span>: SDS main effect와 interaction 동시 제거</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="method-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Secondary Model Tests</h3>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li><span class="highlight">Load × Processing</span>: interaction 제거 모델과 비교</li>
              <li><span class="highlight">All processing terms</span>: processing 관련 항 동시 제거</li>
              <li><span class="highlight">All load terms</span>: load 관련 항 동시 제거</li>
              <li><span class="highlight">Adjusted SDS</span>: SDS 항 제거 모델과 비교</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Random-Effect Summary</h2>

        <div class="card-grid two">
          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Covariance Components</h3>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>Random-intercept variance</li>
              <li>Random-load-slope variance</li>
              <li>Intercept–slope covariance</li>
              <li>Residual variance</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="equation-card">
            <h3 class="card-title">ICC at Mean Load</h3>
            <div class="equation">
              \[
                ICC_{L_c=0}
                =
                \frac{\sigma_{b0}^{2}}
                {\sigma_{b0}^{2}+\sigma_{\varepsilon}^{2}}
              \]
            </div>
            <ul class="text-list">
              <li>ICC: Intraclass Correlation Coefficient</li>
              <li>Load_c = 0, 즉 load 2.5에서 계산</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

